    "promote_external_deepep_column": false,
    "read": "Kimi now has real 20-step MBS1 and MBS2 retained gates. Top-8 standard-EP hot-helper helps over plain standard EP at both MBS points, while Primus-Turbo raw top-k no-helper is faster and lower-memory at MBS1/MBS2. This still does not invalidate the hot-helper mechanism at larger MBS, because Kimi MBS4/MBS8 are not measured yet and DeepSeek MBS8 still favors top-8 helper. Next Kimi work should extend the ladder to MBS4/MBS8 before claiming cross-model highest-MBS behavior."
